            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat, then boil half a kettle</p><p>Squeeze your pouch[es] of the <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong>, making sure to separate the grains</p><p>Once hot, remove the pan off the heat and add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1582890944965-x200.jpg",
