            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan back to the heat and sprinkle your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>into the pan</p><p>Pour in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[380ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and mix it all together</p>",
      "order": 3,
