      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> spinach</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> to the pan (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>",
