    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoked basa & spinach pilau rice </strong>with the<strong> sliced spring onion </strong>sprinkled over the top</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Season<strong> </strong>generously<strong> </strong>with<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
